InPDA (script event)
====================

Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [Game\_class.html game class] type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Returns true if the player is viewing it's PDA.

Usage
-----

*boolean* inPDA( )

Parameters
----------

None.

